    "description": "Are you dying or already robbing?<br><br>GraveyardGambit is an engaging 3D first-person game where you play as a grave robber in a gloomy cemetery. Your mission: dig up and loot graves without being caught by the guards. Use the looted gold to buy upgrades after each round.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/018f5c0bdef2c298ae172a01e1522216.poster.avif?t=1751060864\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/018f5c0bdef2c298ae172a01e1522216.webm?t=1751060864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/018f5c0bdef2c298ae172a01e1522216.mp4?t=1751060864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sneak around the cemetery and dig up graves to collect gold.<br></li><li>Use the gold to buy upgrades and improve your skills.<br></li><li>Avoid the guards – if they see and catch you, you lose the round.<br></li><li>After three captures, the game is lost and you have to start over.<br></li><li>Win a round by successfully escaping the cemetery with the looted gold.<br></li><li>The goal is to complete as many rounds as possible without losing all three lives.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/58b2ec3aaff127e222ee027d1f58858b.poster.avif?t=1751060864\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/58b2ec3aaff127e222ee027d1f58858b.webm?t=1751060864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/58b2ec3aaff127e222ee027d1f58858b.mp4?t=1751060864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Immersive Atmosphere</u>: Experience a dark atmosphere with fog, light, and low-poly graphics.<br></li><li><u>Increasing Difficulty</u>: More guards with new abilities appear as the game progresses.<br></li><li><u>Different Weather Scenarios</u>: Four different weather scenarios offer variety and challenges.<br></li><li><u>Random Events</u>: A large grave appears randomly in each round, offering more loot.<br></li><li><u>Perfect Sound</u>: The sound perfectly complements the atmospheric experience.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/71d6d8d23c343041d42b5cf9ca88c792.poster.avif?t=1751060864\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/71d6d8d23c343041d42b5cf9ca88c792.webm?t=1751060864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102130/extras/71d6d8d23c343041d42b5cf9ca88c792.mp4?t=1751060864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dive into the world of GraveyardGambit and test your skills as a clever grave robber. Can you survive all the rounds and collect the most gold without getting caught?<br><br>Have fun and happy hunting!",
